{"tid":2488710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"產業界震撼，台積電南科晶圓廠跳電 損失數億元","createTime":"2021-04-14T11:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T12:33:05.000Z","uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c3fff84aafd45ff4956d64c4aec8eb16059ce9f7","tid":2488710,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">台積電南科晶圓廠跳電 損失數億元</span></strong><br />\n2021-04-14 17:54 攝影中心 / 記者劉學聖/台南即時報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/14/realtime/12087225.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F14%2Frealtime%2F12087225.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=c2a7c654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於台南的台積電南科晶圓14B-P7廠今天中午傳出停電，讓產業界震撼，業界預估台積電有3萬片晶圓受影響，損失金額在10億元以內，圖為南科台積電14B廠。記者劉學聖／攝影<br />\n<br />\n位於台南的台積電南科晶圓14B-P7廠今天中午傳出停電，讓產業界震撼，台電表示，已與用戶協調同意由另一系統先行轉供，下午4點起已經全面復電，正加壓中，原受損電纜預計明天修復完成。<span class=\"red\">台積電南科P14廠今天受停電影響，業界預估台積電有3萬片晶圓受影響，損失金額在10億元以內。</span><br />\n<br />\n台電表示，南科變電所旁有工程正在施工，工人在廠區地鉚施工作業時，不慎誤損台電161kV地下電纜，導致南科-三福線線路跳脫，並造成台南科學園區C區降壓，台電已與用戶協調同意由另一系統先行轉供，已全面復電，正加壓中，台電嘉南供電處獲報立即動員30多名技術人員、工程師投入迄今，相當辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n由於台積電有保險，實際損失應該可進一步降低。<span class=\"red\">但是因為P14廠主要生產車用電子晶片，這類型晶片供貨吃緊已經一段時間，對全球客戶來說恐怕將會讓新車交程延後。</span>"},{"pid":"66e80d176a1fed7d595452dc7c2f1caaf4d7b5e1","tid":2488710,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"台積電南科廠區跳電影響晶圓生產逾6萬片 今晚已完全復電<br />\n2021/04/14 18:51<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2021/04/14/3499978_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F04%2F14%2F3499978_1.jpg&h=14a7ae1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台積電南科廠區跳電影響晶圓生產逾6萬片，今晚已完全復電。（記者洪友芳攝）"},{"pid":"861489e2c02302ddf692dfb5dd452dbc11076ce6","tid":2488710,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a55a7f60a4e3c441fdc016c1713bcaefe7d21c0","tid":2488710,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:57:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">P14廠主要生產車用電子晶片</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3aabc84cd3e08dd5cf5395e258d14b39a700d19f","tid":2488710,"uid":156936,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:57:56.000Z","msg":"中國特工 斷電偷資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67c163d21bd9d3d9c868c24a23506e7dc96e1c3","tid":2488710,"uid":29514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"好彩放曬D TSM股票"},{"pid":"fd5d34ee56885e757d509ff8e6292516e93e4cd0","tid":2488710,"uid":227588,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"點會咁易跳電？<br />\n好有幻想空間"},{"pid":"1aa9aa375db8a4300d97c0f480dd074cd51dcdaf","tid":2488710,"uid":263183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a67c163d21bd9d3d9c868c24a23506e7dc96e1c3","tid":2488710,"uid":29514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"好彩放曬D TSM股票"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"開市前價格 122.27 +1.00 (0.82%)<br />\nNYSE"},{"pid":"bd554027f2985513686d4d807d02e1936300466e","tid":2488710,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aabc84cd3e08dd5cf5395e258d14b39a700d19f","tid":2488710,"uid":156936,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:57:56.