清。"},{"pid":"153b24f16d75714e165dd5bec0acacb743051d96","tid":2488710,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd5d34ee56885e757d509ff8e6292516e93e4cd0","tid":2488710,"uid":227588,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"點會咁易跳電？<br />\n好有幻想空間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"應該徹查原因"},{"pid":"c79676800e53a40fb72ad4b62da9224b6b1ac31e","tid":2488710,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"南科變電所旁有工程正在施工，工人在廠區地鉚施工作業時<br />\n<br />\n要賠幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdef70d7b1036bbd01b64950345aaa2ee8662a62","tid":2488710,"uid":387391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3aabc84cd3e08dd5cf5395e258d14b39a700d19f","tid":2488710,"uid":156936,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:57:56.000Z","msg":"中國特工 斷電偷資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"一切都是支那人的錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfdf3f051e34ac255e8c05a3bf292fed98fac95","tid":2488710,"uid":262093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a67c163d21bd9d3d9c868c24a23506e7dc96e1c3","tid":2488710,"uid":29514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"好彩放曬D TSM股票"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"一件意外長遠冇乜影響嘅，長榮喺塞住條河之後升得好勁添"},{"pid":"0c8ac7e6eaed50ddc1b194a4bb06c4a849e4371e","tid":2488710,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c79676800e53a40fb72ad4b62da9224b6b1ac31e","tid":2488710,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"南科變電所旁有工程正在施工，工人在廠區地鉚施工作業時<br />\n<br />\n要賠幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,